snippet.title: Kassei - Road Cycling: Steam Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Kassei - Road Cycling is a summer sports simulation game.

To win the yellow jersey you have to manage your team optimally:
as "directeur sportif" you decide on training plans as well as race tactics.

#RoadCyclingTime


Steam Early Access: Starting 23 October 2024
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2331040/Kassei__Road_Cycling/


YouTube:
https://www.youtube.com/@kasseivideos

Website:
https://www.kassei-roadcycling.com/

Twitter:
https://twitter.com/kasseitweets


Music:
Alexander Nakarada - Le Baguette
